              },
              "fullDescription": {
                "text": "Private key material appears to be present in source code.\nRemediation: Remove the key from the repository and rotate/revoke the affected credentials.\nReferences: CWE-321, A02:2021-Cryptographic Failures"
              },
              "help": {
                "text": "Remove the key from the repository and rotate/revoke the affected credentials. (CWE-321) [A02:2021-Cryptographic Failures]"
