                "text": "Insecure SSL/TLS protocol settings"
              },
              "fullDescription": {
                "text": "Older SSL/TLS protocol versions are insecure or deprecated.\nRemediation: Use modern TLS defaults and avoid forcing legacy protocol versions.\nReferences: CWE-326"
              },
              "help": {
                "text": "Use modern TLS defaults and avoid forcing legacy protocol versions. (CWE-326)"
              },
              "properties": {
